    <item>
      <title>中国河北省蔬菜市场火灾造成八人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-04/vegetable-market-fire-in-china-s-hebei-province-kills-eight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当地政府在其官方微信公众号上表示，河北省张家口市发生火灾，造成 8 人死亡，15 人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-04/vegetable-market-fire-in-china-s-hebei-province-kills-eight</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 Jan 2025 08:41:45 GMT</pubDate>
