    <item>
      <title>联邦调查局称拉斯维加斯袭击者患有创伤后应激障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/las-vegas-bomber-suffered-ptsd-and-isn-t-terror-suspect-fbi-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[执法官员称，元旦当天，拉斯维加斯特朗普国际酒店外的爆炸事件中丧生的一位美国陆军绿色贝雷帽士兵患有创伤后应激障碍，并且与恐怖主义没有明显关联。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/las-vegas-bomber-suffered-ptsd-and-isn-t-terror-suspect-fbi-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 23:01:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>战争成本上升，以色列人生活成本紧缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/disheartened-israelis-struggle-with-war-funding-austerity-steps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[税收增加。可支配收入减少。食品、水电费上涨。2025 年伊始，以色列人将面临 400 亿谢克尔（110 亿美元）的战争费用，这可能会加深社会和政治分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/disheartened-israelis-struggle-with-war-funding-austerity-steps</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 14:22:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
